data.description: WELCOME HOME to this 3016 sqft, 4 Bedrooms, 4 bath beauty!!! This home has a large and well maintained above ground swimming pool sitting on .46 acres with enough yard space to run and play, entertain, or to just enjoy yourself by sitting in the yard. This home also has 4 living areas and 2 dining areas. The master's suite has a beautiful bay window. The pictures are nice, but you should COME AND SEE THIS BEAUTIFUL GYM FOR YOURSELF.
